 on June 7, 2023, after being shot while working on a motorcycle delivery inside a commercial store on Tawfiq Ziad Street in Nazareth. Ayman was transported to the English Hospital, where he was pronounced dead after resuscitation attempts failed. Police have launched an investigation into the circumstances of the crime.","review_status":"auto","pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2023-01-01_2023-12-31","enrichment_passes":0,"_pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2023-01-01_2023-12-31","run_id":"canonical","case_index":635}